rmans in as Amalekites, is it a self-fulfilling prophecy that attributes all enemies to Israel as Amalekites, or does the Talmud actually observe goodness in Teutonic peoples for their thwarting the Romans?","filename":"o013","ext":".jpg","w":870,"h":1236,"tn_w":175,"tn_h":250,"tim":1492478613225,"time":1492478613,"md5":"Kp5R5Vf5m6ItgkDcJ90otg==","fsize":191324,"resto":0,"id":"uhhbLvoS","country":"US","m_img":1,"bumplimit":0,"imagelimit":0,"semantic_url":"talmudic-prophecy-and-germamia","country_name":"United States","replies":5,"images":2,"unique_ips":3},{"no":121615674,"now":"04\/17\/17(Mon)21:24:43","name":"Anonymous","com":"<a href=\"#p121615534\" class=\"quotelink\">&gt;&gt;121615534<\/a><br>I meant THIS PIC related.","filename":"1492471486426","ext":".png","w":1793,"h":412,"tn_w":125,"tn_h":28,"tim":1492478683351,"time":1492478683,"md5":"8UsSrr8Ow0\/KT0vS6DMQBA==","fsize":212139,"resto":121615534,"id":"uhhbLvoS","country":"US","country_name":"United States"},{"no":121616309,"now":"04\/17\/17(Mon)21:30:03","name":"Anonymous","com":"<a href=\"#p121615534\" class=\"quotelink\">&gt;&gt;121615534<\/a><br>It is understood to those that know that genetics and memetics are hand in hand. The ramblings of drunk old men and their prophecies mean nothing to me. Even a mixed race (which is every human on the planet) can become pure--not by further biology, but further memetics. Generations of consistently focusing identity and strengthened egos will lead to a new race and &#039;pure&#039; genes. The corrupters are failed experiments, bounding through our social universe like antimatter. They will take eons to disappear, or tremendous energy.","time":1492479003,"resto":121615534,"id":"qlSTNrcm","country":"US","country_name":"United States"},{"no":121616965,"now":"04\/17\/17(Mon)21:35:14","name":"Anonymous","com":"<a href=\"#p121616309\" class=\"quotelink\">&gt;&gt;121616309<\/a><br>Will anime forge that path, or break us?","filename":"1488003920701","ext":".jpg","w":683,"h"